- Cell magic: operate on multiple lines of input. Prefix by double '%%'

Shell commands: Prefix with '!'. E.x. directory = !pwd # ['/Users/riteshraj/Documents/ritesh-github-portfolio-monorepo']
Shell-like magic command: E.x. `%cat`, `%cp`, `%ls`, `%mkdir`, etc. These shell-like magic commands can also be used without `%` sign by toggling `%automagic` magic function.
NOTE: `!cd..` does nothing because shell commands are executed in a temporary sub-shell. To make it work use `%cd` magic command.
